---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Safety & Hygiene Standards | Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura"
  description="Explore how Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura maintains 24x7 security, CCTV oversight, and hospital-grade hygiene routines for girl students."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Girls PG near Osmanpura</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Safety &amp; Hygiene Standards</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Parents trust Jyoti Girls PG because every corridor, room, and service is designed to keep young women secure, healthy, and focused on their goals.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Round-the-Clock Security Oversight</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Supervised Entry &amp; CCTV</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">CCTV coverage in common areas and a resident warden ensure every movement is monitored without intruding on privacy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Documented Visitor Protocols</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Visitors are verified, logged, and accompanied in shared zones. Parents receive immediate updates for late-night permissions or special approvals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Emergency Ready Infrastructure</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Fire alarms, extinguishers, and evacuation drills keep residents prepared. Nearby clinics in Osmanpura are on-call for quick medical assistance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Hospital-Level Hygiene Practices</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Daily Sanitisation Routines</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Housekeeping teams disinfect washrooms and dining spaces thrice a day, with deep-clean cycles scheduled every weekend.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Laundry &amp; Linen Control</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Dedicated laundry staff handle washing and ironing, while bedding is rotated based on a documented calendar shared with parents.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Water Purity Checks</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">RO and UV filtration units are serviced monthly. Water quality reports are pinned on the notice board for complete transparency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Resident Wellness &amp; Support</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">First-aid kits on every floor along with tie-ups for doctor-on-call visits.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Well-lit study halls and staircases reduce fatigue and late-night anxiety.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Periodic health camps covering nutrition, posture, and stress management.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Guardian alerts for illness or extended rest requirements.</li>
      </ul>
      <div style="margin-top:40px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="visit">Schedule a safety walkthrough</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20schedule%20a%20safety%20tour." class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Message our warden</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
